@startuml state-maintenance-request
skinparam dpi 150
skinparam pageMargin 10
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam stateFontSize 12
skinparam stateAttributeFontSize 10

title Maintenance Request State Machine

[*] --> New : CreateMaintenanceRequest

state New : Request submitted by member.\nRequestedByProfileId, Address,\nPhone, Description recorded.

state Received : Staff acknowledges request.\nReceivedByProfileId, ReceivedByName,\nReceivedDate recorded.

state Started : Work in progress.\nWorkStarted timestamp recorded.\nUnitEntered mode recorded.

state Completed : Work finished.\nWorkCompleted timestamp recorded.\nWorkCompletedByName recorded.

New --> Received : ReceiveMaintenanceRequest\n(staff acknowledges, records\nReceivedByProfileId, ReceivedDate)

Received --> Started : StartMaintenanceRequest\n(records WorkStarted,\nUnitEntered)

Started --> Completed : CompleteMaintenanceRequest\n(records WorkCompleted,\nWorkCompletedByName)

Completed --> [*]

note right of New
  Forward-only transitions enforced.
  No backward state changes permitted.
end note

note bottom of Started
  UnitEntered values:
  - MemberAtHome
  - MemberNotAtHome
  - EmergencyEntryRequired
end note
@enduml
